{
  "stem": "12494.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He got together with some other parents who have sent their Jewish children to Switzerland, in a manner similar to the way he and my mother did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after World War II broke out in September, they decided that Hungary will, in all likelihood, stay out of the war, but that Switzerland would be crushed between Germany and Italy, and that, therefore, their kids would be better off to return to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so about a dozen of us-- various families unrelated to each other-- were gathered together and we started the trek in late September, 1939, via Italy and Yugoslavia-- you couldn't go through Germany anymore-- back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was an interesting trip, but I won't go into the details.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's the way we got back Hungary in late September, 1939.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the answer is yes and no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born in 1925.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I was fairly mature for my age, And my dad did confide in me fairly early.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I wasn't home much at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to Yeshiva in 19-- see, immediately after my return from Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In late 1939, I went to Yeshiva and from '39 to-- '39 to early '42, I spent most of my time in Yeshiva, in [INAUDIBLE] and in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rest of the time when I was home, I tried always to cram in the year's studies, the year's secular studies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In typically six weeks to get-- get through my examination, my state examination, to be qualified for a higher grade.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we went on vacation, and-- so I really wasn't aware of much in-- in-- in Jewish life, in Jewish crisis life, until about March 1942.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's when I was almost 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
